content: Best skin I've ever used.
Outstanding!
So beautiful + worth every penny...very good support and frequently updated by John!

Heh, who said gradients were out of style? Flat design, step aside! If you're like me and prefer that, this is for you! Liv Dark gives many gradients, background colors, and some fonts to mix and match to fit your style! You can even show your wallpaper behind Poweramp. If I have one complaint, some of the fonts are rather basic compared to the stylish other ones. A custom font option would be great! Overall, I recommend Liv Dark for Poweramp. It'll probably stay as my theme for a long time!
